          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Diplomatic Personnel Modernization Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of State to provide Congress with a five-year staffing plan. The plan shall contain certain information, including a set of comprehensive workforce data and recommendations on the number of Foreign Service officers, disaggregated by service cone, that should be posted at each foreign mission. </p> <p><br /></p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-04-02T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-10-01T20:12:36Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
